snippet.title: JUMP FORCE - Join the JUMP FORCE Launch Trailer | XB1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Earth depends on YOU! Unite to Fight with your favorite Shonen Jump characters to defend our planet from chaos and destruction!

Pre-Order the JUMP FORCE Ultimate Edition now to get 3 Days Early Access to the game: http://bandainam.co/JumpForcePO

#JumpForce #UniteToFight #BandaiNamco
